MADHOUSE
  Industrial Port - Defuse Scenario

Counter-Terrorists: 
Defend the Fuel Depot(A) and Refinment 
Facilities (B) from terrorists. Prevent the 
terrorists from planting their destructive
device and stop them in their tracks.

Terrorists: 
Navigate your way through the train yard, 
Industrial area, or residences to reach
the Fuel Depot (A) or the Refinery(B). 
Destory either target or eliminate all CTs.
 
Other Notes: There are two objective sites
within this level.
